<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="steal-v">steal <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /stiːl/    美 /stiːl/  </p>
<p>(stole, stolen) vt &amp; vi</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>偷；窃取：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I’m terribly sad because my new bicycle was stolen yesterday.
昨天我的新自行车被偷了，我很难过。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The passing years <strong>steal from</strong> us one thing after another.
逝去的年华从我们这里偷走一样又一样东西。</p><footer>——贺拉斯</footer></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>偷偷地移动；偷偷地进行：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>steal a glance</strong> at
偷看一眼</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He <strong>stole out of</strong> the house without anyone seeing him.
他偷偷溜出了房子，没人发觉。</p></div></div>